Text: "I begin alone.from DRCongo\n\nGoing To zimbabwe by bus. Passing by zimbia it\
  \ take two 2 days\nI enjoy it \nWe leave at 8h30. Changing 3 buses\nO Explore The\
  \ flores bushes in Zambia\nPassing all nigth. In The buse\nIt a very Long way\n\
  In.The Zambia We take a rest \n\nGood experience in The life Travelling with unknow\
  \ people\nWe pass good.moment like family\nWhen i arrived in zimbabwe\nWe are going\
  \ in the church\nWhere there was an.organisation\nStay there 4 days\nAfter That\
  \ We visiting 6 sites of Women organisation\nThen we went to victoria falls\n\n\
  Stay 2 days there and returned home\nBy fligth\nI was happy to be part of this"
